                    "text-1": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>At Dekorvibe, we aim to make the returns and replacements process simple and transparent.</p><ul><li>Return and replacement requests are accepted within 24 hours of delivery. To ensure a smooth review process, please contact our Customer Support team within this timeframe.</li><li>Items should be unused, in their original packaging, and accompanied by all included accessories, parts, manuals, and inserts (where applicable)</li><li>All requests are reviewed with our return and replacement team to ensure the easy resolution.</li><li>For any questions regarding return, product concerns, or the return process, please contact our support team for assistance.</li></ul><p><strong>Email:</strong> support@dekorvibe.com<br><strong>Support Hours:</strong> Monday to Saturday, 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM.</p>",
